on Friday is largely a lecture
demonstration, displaying

01:16.000 --> 01:21.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
how dance is really ideas,
that it's thought made visible,
in the same way that music is

01:22.766 --> 01:26.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
thought made audible.

01:26.000 --> 01:31.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Our hope is that the
mind will be stirred and
the heart will be moved.

